{"tid":1376164,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"未來60日關鍵時候","createTime":"2019-07-28T09:02:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T09:02:41.000Z","uid":71071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0407a29d0340a3f306eca191915b8ee20673cd55","tid":1376164,"uid":71071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T09:02:41.000Z","msg":"最壞的情況是香港實施戒嚴，如是者將引發大量資本和人才外逃。<br />\n<br />\n報告指出，香港正面對前所未有的政治危機，...<br />\n<br />\n大和認為，如果戒嚴或緊急狀態只維持數周，示威者很可能會在令狀結束後再度上街。因此，一旦實施便難以退卻，戒嚴或者緊急狀態可能歷時數以月計，此或有大量的資本和人才逃離香港，對香港的經濟和國際金融中心地位造成高度負面影響。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/hongkong/article/2201321/%E5%A4%A7%E5%92%8C%3A%E6%9C%AA%E4%BE%8660%E6%97%A5%E9%97%9C%E9%8D%B5+%E6%9C%80%E5%A3%9E%E6%83%85%E6%B3%81%E6%B8%AF%E6%88%96%E5%AF%A6%E6%96%BD%E6%88%92%E5%9A%B4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fhongkong%2Farticle%2F2201321%2F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%2592%258C%253A%25E6%259C%25AA%25E4%25BE%258660%25E6%2597%25A5%25E9%2597%259C%25E9%258D%25B5%2B%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25A3%259E%25E6%2583%2585%25E6%25B3%2581%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%2588%2596%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E6%2596%25BD%25E6%2588%2592%25E5%259A%25B4&d=9l2h7zKZEd5x%2FdYTAZY3wkBo7c%2BYFxEppcXi0rJe94o%3D&h=9641952b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/hongkong/article/2201321/%E5%A4%A7%E5%92%8C%3A%E6%9C%AA%E4%BE%8660%E6%97%A5%E9%97%9C%E9%8D%B5+%E6%9C%80%E5%A3%9E%E6%83%85%E6%B3%81%E6%B8%AF%E6%88%96%E5%AF%A6%E6%96%BD%E6%88%92%E5%9A%B4</a><br />\n<br />\ncome on baby, 等咗好耐"}]}